Currency details GYD Guyana [Guyanese dollar]

Label of currency GYD is Guyanese dollar.

Currency code GYD is associated to Guyana, flag is used on this site for it.

Amounts in this currency have up to 2 decimals.

It is mainly associated to country or zone Guyana.

Currency code GYD is a 3 letter normalized code according to standard ISO-4217, the 2 first letters are the code of the issuing country, third letter is the initial of the currency.

We recorded price on this currency since 1960-01-01
